far militerishe zakhn.

00:18:06.952 --> 00:18:09.084
un di daytshn hobn undz gehit andere.

00:18:09.158 --> 00:18:13.117
dortn iz gedenk ikh, ikh veys nit tsi mayn shvester veyst fun dem. zi iz nit geven.

00:18:13.258 --> 00:18:17.791
nor eyner, eyner a BOY bay undz, mitn nomen Kazlovski, kh'hob dokh dermont zikh in im

00:18:17.933 --> 00:18:20.306
er iz geven a fun SHOMER HATSAIR.

00:18:20.700 --> 00:18:24.237
hot er gezogt azoy, a- az mir veln nokh, az undzer blut vet nit shvaygn.

00:18:24.312 --> 00:18:27.276
undzer blut vet nit shvaygn. mir veln nokh nemen nekome fun aykh.

00:18:27.450 --> 00:18:29.944
un er, un er hot dos nit farshtanen, nor er hot gezogt

00:18:29.944 --> 00:18:32.911
"vos hot er geredt? vos, er hot epes geredt oyf undz."

00:18:33.036 --> 00:18:34.667
un m'hot im oyfgehangen.

00:18:34.926 --> 00:18:36.962
er hot dos gezogt tsu a daytshn?

00:18:34.943 --> 00:18:36.101
⟨der BOY⟩

00:18:36.478 --> 00:18:38.974
er hot gezogt tsu undz, tsi er hot geredt azoy vi a

00:18:38.974 --> 00:18:40.684
nit tsu d- mir hobn ale ge-

00:18:39.583 --> 00:18:43.610
oh, er hot dos gezogt tsun aykh, un, un der daytsh hot gefregt

00:18:41.136 --> 00:18:43.844
hot er geredt tsu un- hot gehert.

00:18:43.844 --> 00:18:45.884
ye, un er hot gefregt vos er hot geredt.

00:18:45.884 --> 00:18:48.065
er hot gezogt az undzer blut vet nit shvaygn.

00:18:48.139 --> 00:18:51.232
mir nemen nekome, far yeder, far yeder eynem.

00:18:50.029 --> 00:18:52.402
m'hot im glaykh gehongen?

00:18:51.232 --> 00:18:52.405
oyfgehangen.

00:18:52.405 --> 00:18:54.934
m'hot aroysgerufn tsu alemen, m'hot undz gevizn

00:18:54.957 --> 00:18:56.689
vi azoy er iz oyfgehangen gevorn.

00:18:56.880 --> 00:19:00.249
er hot a bruder gehat, Mates, ikh veys nit tsi er hot gel- geblibn lebn.

00:19:00.677 --> 00:19:03.354
er iz geven a yingl fun nayntsn akhtsn yor mistome.

00:19:04.035 --> 00:19:06.307
ah fun HASHOMER HATSAIR iz er geven

00:19:06.735 --> 00:19:08.099
hot men im oyfgehangen

00:19:08.099 --> 00:19:12.939
un, un dernokh zaynen mir geve- mir dortn geve- arbet, iz dortn iz men krank gevorn oyf tifus.

00:19:12.945 --> 00:19:15.588
ale gezunte ment- mener zaynen krank gevorn.

00:19:15.544 --> 00:19:17.613
ir hot gelitn aleyn fun tifus?

00:19:16.860 --> 00:19:17.971
ikh nit.

00:19:17.971 --> 00:19:20.460
nor di mener, merstn teyl. shtarke mener.

00:19:20.460 --> 00:19:23.497
a shmid a gezunter ⟨hot mit zey⟩ geleygt, iz men shoyn nit oyfgeshtanen.

00:19:23.497 --> 00:19:25.038
un ikh hob gehat a lerer

00:19:25.213 --> 00:19:27.569
fun undzer shtetl, Segalovitsh hot er geheysn

00:19:27.897 --> 00:19:29.781
oy, aza fayner lerer

00:19:30.175 --> 00:19:34.295
er hot alemen geredt tsu alemen, getreyst alemen, gekumen tsu alemen

00:19:34.295 --> 00:19:38.090
un der- un dernokh iz er nebekh krank gevorn un geshtorbn.

00:19:37.465 --> 00:19:39.129
a sakh zenen gefaln?

00:19:38.764 --> 00:19:39.871
geshtorbn.

00:19:40.266 --> 00:19:41.579
zaynen geshtorbn.

00:19:40.823 --> 00:19:43.483
geshtorbn fun, fun krankeyt

00:19:41.579 --> 00:19:44.369
geshtorbn fun tifus. fun krankeyt.

00:19:44.164 --> 00:19:46.233
esn hot men genug gehat?

00:19:44.369 --> 00:19:47.789
un zey flegn zayn, zey flegn zayn krank, flegn zey reydn azoy

00:19:47.789 --> 00:19:49.509
az ikh vel nokh araynhargenen

00:19:49.509 --> 00:19:50.639
dem, dem

00:19:50.639 --> 00:19:52.449
dem kukh, geven a grober

00:19:52.449 --> 00:19:54.049
ikh vel im derhargenen

00:19:54.049 --> 00:19:56.460
un ikh ave- mir veln avekgeyn ale in partizaner

00:19:56.483 --> 00:19:57.906
zey hobn nit gevust vos zey reydn.

00:19:57.906 --> 00:20:01.640
az mir geyn in partizaner, un mir zoln do n- keyner fun undz nit blaybn.

00:20:02.254 --> 00:20:05.015
a sakh zaynen geshtorbn, ye- shtarke mener.

00:20:05.038 --> 00:20:07.479
m'hot gehat genug tsum esn demolt?

00:20:07.097 --> 00:20:09.203
esn hot men gegebn. s'iz geven a kukh

00:20:09.203 --> 00:20:12.359
zey hobn gekokht di ferdishe fleysh, hot men gezogt, az me kokht

00:20:12.359 --> 00:20:15.286
gepeygerte fer- fl- fun ferdishe fleysh brengt men

00:20:15.286 --> 00:20:17.098
hot men gegebn zu- esn

00:20:17.138 --> 00:20:19.494
ober d- mir hobn nokh gehat di familyes

00:20:20.040 --> 00:20:21.536
in, in der heym.

00:20:21.677 --> 00:20:23.831
undzere mishpokhes zaynen dokh geblibn in der heym.

00:20:23.938 --> 00:20:25.670
ir hot gehat kontakt mit zey?

00:20:24.799 --> 00:20:27.319
e- hobn mir gehat kontakt mit zey.

00:20:27.319 --> 00:20:32.995
me a- andere ⟨flegn⟩ shi- m- hot men gehat rekht tsu shikn peklekh, esn oykhet.

00:20:27.583 --> 00:20:28.674
vi azoy?

00:20:32.629 --> 00:20:34.684
un brivlekh hot men geshikt?

00:20:33.034 --> 00:20:36.414
glaykh fun onheyb on, un brivlekh, ye

00:20:34.684 --> 00:20:35.964
ahin un tsurik?

00:20:36.414 --> 00:20:41.635
es iz geven dor- un dortn, vos hobn zey geton dortn? zey hobn oyfgeklibn ale fun arumike shtetlekh

00:20:41.742 --> 00:20:43.409
di eltere mentshn

00:20:43.409 --> 00:20:45.122
ale alte mentshn

00:20:45.122 --> 00:20:47.625
un i- di vos zaynen nit feik tsu der arbet

00:20:47.715 --> 00:20:50.662
un me hot alemen derharget oyf ⟨Zhilonke⟩.

00:20:50.888 --> 00:20:53.059
UNK gemakht a groysn keyver

00:20:53.183 --> 00:20:57.913
un me hot zey alemen derharge- ve- mayn mame iz geven a yunge, tsvey un fertsik yor

00:20:57.913 --> 00:20:59.955
iz zi arayngefaln mit di eltere mentshn.

00:20:59.955 --> 00:21:01.946
zi hot oysgezen zogn zey shlekht

00:21:01.946 --> 00:21:02.916
alt

00:21:02.916 --> 00:21:06.204
un zi iz gegangen mit tsvey kinder, mit di shvester un ⟨mitn bruder⟩

00:21:06.548 --> 00:21:10.980
un m'hot genumen di mamen. me hot ir, m- di mamen, un di boben

00:21:11.003 --> 00:21:14.608
un di mame's shvester. alemen in furn hot men gefirt zey.

00:21:14.665 --> 00:21:16.703
di goyim hobn gezogt, er ⟨hot⟩ dertseylt

00:21:16.703 --> 00:21:19.434
az m'hot zey gefirt in a groyse shtal zaynen zey geven

00:21:19.525 --> 00:21:21.631
un tsu fuftsik man a PARTY

00:21:21.631 --> 00:21:23.180
hot men gefirt tsu di griber.

00:21:22.866 --> 00:21:23.805
tsu vo-

00:21:23.507 --> 00:21:25.019
tsu fuftsik mentshn

00:21:25.110 --> 00:21:26.690
hot men gefirt tsu di griber.

00:21:26.865 --> 00:21:29.663
s'iz geven oysgegrobn a grub. ikh bin geven UNK ⟨nokhn krig⟩ UNK

00:21:29.663 --> 00:21:32.127
i- itstert UNK a groysn monument.

00:21:32.127 --> 00:21:34.166
u- un mayn mame hot gehat gold.

00:21:34.527 --> 00:21:36.304
mir ⟨zaynen⟩ nit geven keyn raykhe mentshn

00:21:36.304 --> 00:21:40.055
nor gold hot men ale mol gehaltn in ⟨ZAPAS⟩ UNK

00:21:39.285 --> 00:21:40.730
bahaltn oyf zikh?

00:21:40.264 --> 00:21:42.809
ye, gehaltn a torbitshke gold hot zi gehat bay zikh.

00:21:42.809 --> 00:21:45.405
di kinder ⟨hot zi dokh⟩ nit gekent gebn, kleyne kinder

00:21:45.613 --> 00:21:49.049
un ikh bin geven avek, hob ikh gemeynt ikh kum in tsvey monatn tsurik.

00:21:49.242 --> 00:21:51.082
zi hot gezogt mir farn geyn

00:21:51.082 --> 00:21:54.992
"nem a zeygerl, nem a fingerl. efsher vet zikh aroyskumen baytn bay goyim

00:21:54.992 --> 00:21:59.022
mistome." zog ikh "mame, in tsvey monatn arum zogn zey, dray monatn, kum ikh tsurik.

00:21:59.022 --> 00:22:02.240
⟨hobn zey undz gezogt⟩ az mir veln nit, nor oyf dray monatn UNK

00:22:02.240 --> 00:22:04.830
hob ikh gornisht nit genumen. ikh y- ershtns, mayn mame

00:22:04.830 --> 00:22:07.820
hob ikh gezogt, az zi darf ⟨hobn gikher⟩ fun mir. zi hot kinder mit zikh.

00:22:07.568 --> 00:22:10.380
un mitn gold hot zi geratevet dos lebn?

00:22:08.003 --> 00:22:09.134
UNK

00:22:09.134 --> 00:22:14.205
di gold hot zi gehat a gantse torbele. azoy vi m'hot derharget ir, UNK hot men di ⟨goldekhts⟩ tsugenumen.

00:22:14.205 --> 00:22:15.645
kinder hobn mir gornisht nit gehat.

00:22:15.752 --> 00:22:17.315
nit bay ir, ale yidn

00:22:17.524 --> 00:22:19.408
m'hot geheysn oyston nakete

00:22:19.667 --> 00:22:23.958
un di goyim hobn dertseylt az di erd hot ho- ho- hot ge⟨tsaplt⟩

00:22:23.958 --> 00:22:27.806
andere nit tsugeharget. di goyim UNK ⟨arum hot men dertseylt hobn gekent hern di gvaldn⟩

00:22:27.806 --> 00:22:28.807
di geshreyen.

00:22:29.252 --> 00:22:31.780
itstert dertseylt men mayn shvester, eyne iz geven

00:22:31.780 --> 00:22:33.754
ho- iz dortn do a poylishe goye

00:22:33.754 --> 00:22:36.986
vos zi geyt oyf dem ort, un ale yor makht zi a

00:22:36.986 --> 00:22:39.590
 brengt zi kinder fun SCHOOL

00:22:39.698 --> 00:22:40.791
in dem ort

00:22:40.791 --> 00:22:42.661
un zi makht a hazkore a groyse.

00:22:42.870 --> 00:22:44.014
UNK di

00:22:44.014 --> 00:22:46.239
di poylishe goye nemt CARE oyfn ort.

00:22:45.823 --> 00:22:46.947
un ah

00:22:47.123 --> 00:22:50.475
ver iz geven mit ayer ma- ver iz geven mit ayer mame?

00:22:47.815 --> 00:22:49.769
m'hot derharget ale ⟨umetum⟩

00:22:49.769 --> 00:22:50.959
mayn mame

00:22:50.959 --> 00:22:52.410
oyfn fur hobn zey geforn

00:22:52.410 --> 00:22:55.841
un di bobe hot men tsugenumen, di mame's ma- shvester

00:22:56.269 --> 00:22:58.308
ot di, ot di dray hot men tsugenumen

00:22:58.308 --> 00:23:00.824
un mayne a shvester iz geven UNK feik un iz gelofn

00:23:00.824 --> 00:23:03.214
un zi hot zikh gebetn, in a shul hot men zey avekgefirt

00:23:03.214 --> 00:23:06.003
un zi hot zikh gebetn bay di daytshn az di sh- mayn ma-

00:23:06.003 --> 00:23:09.445
un zi hot gerisn di, di tir UNK

00:23:09.445 --> 00:23:12.244
azoy, un s'hot gornisht nit geholfn

00:23:12.672 --> 00:23:15.197
un di shvester un briderl geblibn aleyn

00:23:15.422 --> 00:23:17.778
un mayn shvester bashraybt do in dem bikhl

00:23:17.953 --> 00:23:20.532
un un, m'hot tsugenumen di ale mentshn un derharget.

00:23:20.532 --> 00:23:24.709
s'iz ongekumen fun andere el- eltern UNK kinder. di eltern hobn geshikt

00:23:24.709 --> 00:23:27.662
peklekh, esn geven

00:23:27.662 --> 00:23:31.329
iz vemen s'iz ongekumen iz ongekumen. un tsu mir iz oykh ongekumen

00:23:31.403 --> 00:23:33.804
un di shvester hot gesh- geshribn mir in brivl

00:23:33.804 --> 00:23:36.133
az di mame lebt, zolt zikh nit zorgn

00:23:36.133 --> 00:23:38.890
un ikh shik dir a pekl, a pekele, a pekl esn.

00:23:37.883 --> 00:23:39.311
un s'iz geven a lign?

00:23:38.890 --> 00:23:41.450
s'iz geven nit rikhtik. zi hot nit gevelt mir onzogn.

00:23:41.207 --> 00:23:43.901
vos iz gevorn mit ayer bruder in der tsayt?

00:23:41.900 --> 00:23:43.276
⟨vos zi hot mir⟩ geshikt.

00:23:43.418 --> 00:23:46.685
der bruderl iz geven, m- i- shvester mitn briderl zaynen geblibn in geto.

00:23:46.742 --> 00:23:47.886
di yunge kinder.

00:23:47.886 --> 00:23:50.333
der d- der front hot zikh genumen dernentern.

00:23:50.333 --> 00:23:55.278
di daytshn zaynen, hobn ge- genumen krign mapoles, fun, fun milkhome

00:23:55.278 --> 00:23:58.143
hobn zey gevelt likvidirn di yidn, nit ibergelozn di yidn.

00:23:57.576 --> 00:23:59.561
dos iz arum dray un fertsik?

00:23:59.162 --> 00:24:00.188
ye.

00:24:00.188 --> 00:24:02.019
hobn nit gevelt iberlozn di yidn

00:24:02.019 --> 00:24:04.320
hobn zey genumen likvidirn di getos

00:24:04.360 --> 00:24:06.753
hot a teyl avekgeshikt nokh Kovne.

00:24:06.753 --> 00:24:08.443
m'hot zey nit gefirt in Kovne. m'hot zey

00:24:08.443 --> 00:24:09.580
glaykh derharget

00:24:09.580 --> 00:24:10.783
i- oyf di fortn.

00:24:11.363 --> 00:24:13.621
un a teyl, un mayn shvester hot gezogt

00:24:13.621 --> 00:24:15.795
az zi hot a shvester in di lagern

00:24:15.987 --> 00:24:19.103
az zi vil nit geyn oyf Kovne, zi vet geyn tsu mayn, tsu di shvester.

00:24:19.193 --> 00:24:21.229
hot men, hot men geshikt ir tsu mir.

00:24:21.589 --> 00:24:25.526
iz i- mitn briderl. beyde. zaynen zey beyde gekumen tsu mir

00:24:21.673 --> 00:24:23.017
un ayer bruder?

00:24:25.526 --> 00:24:28.181
in in Zhezhmerer lager. beyde zaynen gekumen.

00:24:27.900 --> 00:24:29.531
kedey tsu arbetn?

00:24:29.098 --> 00:24:31.758
 zayne-, m- m'hot zey arayngeshikt tsu undz, ober

00:24:31.758 --> 00:24:33.908
bay undz iz shoyn di arbet geven geendikt.

00:24:33.938 --> 00:24:36.107
m'hot shoyn durkh a yor tsayt hot shoyn oysgeboyt di ve-

00:24:36.107 --> 00:24:38.627
di veg. s'iz shoyn nit geven di arbet oykh nit tsu fil.

00:24:38.700 --> 00:24:41.394
hot men genumen trakhtn vos tsu ton mit undz.

00:24:41.603 --> 00:24:44.330
iz aropgekumen eyn mol politsey a yidisher

00:24:44.640 --> 00:24:46.524
ongeton in bloye zakhn

00:24:46.918 --> 00:24:50.894
mit groyse ⟨hits⟩, mit di mogn Dovids oyf di hent, un, mundirn.

00:24:51.087 --> 00:24:53.882
un zey hobn zey aropgerufn plats, un zey hobn gezogt az

00:24:53.972 --> 00:24:56.075
me zogt "avu mir kumen

00:24:56.149 --> 00:24:57.932
firn mir durkh aktsyonen."

00:24:57.938 --> 00:24:59.754
mir hobn shoyn gehert di mayses.

00:24:59.946 --> 00:25:03.351
"nor mir firn nit keyn aktsyonen. mir darfn aykh hobn

00:25:03.351 --> 00:25:05.593
oyf arbet oyf di fortn.

00:25:05.987 --> 00:25:07.595
mir nemen aykh oyf arbet.

00:25:07.595 --> 00:25:10.759
hundert fuftsik mentshn, mir

00:25:10.759 --> 00:25:13.763
iz UNK yunge mener

00:25:13.763 --> 00:25:15.409
vos zey hobn gedarft ton dortn

00:25:15.409 --> 00:25:16.545
oysgrobn

00:25:16.703 --> 00:25:18.907
di griber, dortn oyf Ponar

00:25:18.930 --> 00:25:21.960
un zey hobn gedarft brenen di kerpers. zey hobn gevelt

00:25:21.960 --> 00:25:25.140
di daytshn far- zol zayn, zol men nit visn vos zey hobn opgeton.

00:25:25.157 --> 00:25:26.731
hot men, hot men genumen mener

00:25:26.731 --> 00:25:29.466
fun undz oyf tsu arbetn dortn oyf di, oyfn Ponar.

00:25:29.466 --> 00:25:30.585
oyf di

00:25:30.169 --> 00:25:32.222
der man hot dos dertseylt?

00:25:30.861 --> 00:25:31.659
ah ye.

00:25:31.659 --> 00:25:35.414
zey, dos iz shoyn geven di shpeter UNK, shpeter az s'zol nit zayn keyn shpurn

00:25:35.414 --> 00:25:36.559
vos zey hobn opgeton.

00:25:36.565 --> 00:25:38.907
azoy iz geven in Kovner geto oykh geven.

00:25:38.907 --> 00:25:42.450
kedey b- UNK me flegt hern dem ⟨roykh⟩ fun vaytn

00:25:41.695 --> 00:25:44.406
iz vos hot pasirt mit aykh in der tsayt?

00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:46.661
iz gekumen, iz gekumen di shvester un briderl tsu mir

00:25:46.661 --> 00:25:48.084
in Zhezhmerer lager.

00:25:48.107 --> 00:25:52.846
un, un Zhezhmerer lager hot men, iz shoyn geven bald tsu likvidirn, ⟨iz shoyn⟩ nit geven keyn arbet

00:25:52.846 --> 00:25:55.200
hot men a kley- a, nit keyn sakh gelozn

00:25:55.200 --> 00:25:58.091
un mir hot men genumen shikn mentshn oyf arbet

00:25:58.198 --> 00:26:01.199
oyf, bay di torf arbetn arum Kovne b-

00:26:01.199 --> 00:26:02.625
epes in farsheydene erter.

00:26:02.625 --> 00:26:04.166
mir hobn zey nit gekent shikn

00:26:04.189 --> 00:26:06.810
vayl ikh hob a shvester mit briderl, hob ⟨ikh⟩ nit gevelt

00:26:06.810 --> 00:26:08.874
hobn zey mir avekgeshikt in Kovner geto.

00:26:09.184 --> 00:26:10.848
mitn shvester un bruderl?

00:26:09.893 --> 00:26:10.767
ye.

00:26:10.767 --> 00:26:14.139
bin ikh ongekumen zen shoyn.

00:26:11.597 --> 00:26:15.219
vu, vu zayt ir ongekumen? oyf velkher gas, veyst ir?

00:26:14.635 --> 00:26:18.679
 m'hot mir gebrakht in a MOVIE. kino ⟨LITANIKA⟩ hot dos geheysn.

00:26:18.718 --> 00:26:19.761
a kino.

00:26:19.697 --> 00:26:20.585
kino?

00:26:19.761 --> 00:26:21.696
vos m'hot, m'hot gemakht in deroyf

00:26:21.696 --> 00:26:23.096
in a MOVIE, dos iz a kino

00:26:23.096 --> 00:26:25.816
un m'hot gemakht dortn

00:26:25.816 --> 00:26:27.556
m'hot gemakht nares

